---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contact" description="Get in touch with State of Forms for data analytics and engineering solutions">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Get in Touch</h1>
      <p>Let's discuss how we can help transform your data</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Form Section -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: start;">
        <!-- Contact Form -->
        <div>
          <h2>Send Us a Message</h2>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
            Fill out the form below and we'll get back to you within 24 hours.
          </p>

          <form action="#" method="POST" style="max-width: 500px;">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="name">Name *</label>
              <input 
                type="text" 
                id="name" 
                name="name" 
                required 
                placeholder="Your name"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="email">Email *</label>
              <input 
                type="email" 
                id="email" 
                name="email" 
                required 
                placeholder="your.email@example.com"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="company">Company</label>
              <input 
                type="text" 
                id="company" 
                name="company" 
                placeholder="Your company name (optional)"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="service">Service Interest</label>
              <select id="service" name="service">
                <option value="">Select a service...</option>
                <option value="analytics">Data Analytics & Reporting</option>
                <option value="engineering">Data Pipeline Engineering</option>
                <option value="bi">Business Intelligence</option>
                <option value="custom">Custom Development</option>
                <option value="consulting">Consulting</option>
                <option value="other">Other</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="budget">Budget Range</label>
              <select id="budget" name="budget">
                <option value="">Select a range (optional)...</option>
                <option value="small">Under $10,000</option>
                <option value="medium">$10,000 - $50,000</option>
                <option value="large">$50,000 - $100,000</option>
                <option value="enterprise">$100,000+</option>
                <option value="discuss">Prefer to discuss</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="message">Project Description *</label>
              <textarea 
                id="message" 
                name="message" 
                required 
                placeholder="Tell us about your project and what you're looking to accomplish..."
              ></textarea>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 100%; cursor: pointer;">
                Send Message
              </button>
            </div>

            <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 1rem;">
              * Required fields
            </p>
          </form>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact Information -->
        <div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Contact Information</h3>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
              We're here to help you unlock the potential of your data.
            </p>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
              <h4 style="color: #2563eb; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">üìß Email</h4>
              <p style="margin: 0;">
                <a href="mailto:info@stateofforms.com" style="color: #1f2937;">
                  info@stateofforms.com
                </a>
              </p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
              <h4 style="color: #2563eb; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">‚è±Ô∏è Response Time</h4>
              <p style="margin: 0;">We typically respond within 24 hours on business days</p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
              <h4 style="color: #2563eb; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">üîó Connect With Us</h4>
              <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
                <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-secondary" style="text-decoration: none;">
                  LinkedIn
                </a>
                <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-secondary" style="text-decoration: none;">
                  GitHub
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card" style="margin-top: 2rem; background: #f9fafb;">
            <h3>What Happens Next?</h3>
            <ol style="padding-left: 1.5rem;">
              <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
                <strong>We'll review your inquiry</strong> and respond within 24 hours
              </li>
              <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
                <strong>Schedule a consultation</strong> to discuss your needs in detail
              </li>
              <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
                <strong>Receive a proposal</strong> outlining our approach and timeline
              </li>
              <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
                <strong>Start building</strong> your data solution together
              </li>
            </ol>
          </div>

          <div class="card" style="margin-top: 2rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white;">
            <h3 style="color: white;">Featured Platform</h3>
            <p style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);">
              Check out QueryForge, our production analytics platform showcasing 
              real-time financial data visualization.
            </p>
            <a 
              href="https://queryforge.ai" 
              target="_blank" 
              rel="noopener" 
              class="btn btn-secondary" 
              style="margin-top: 1rem; display: inline-block; background: white; color: #667eea;"
            >
              Visit QueryForge ‚Üí
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      
      <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 3rem auto 0;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>What types of projects do you take on?</h3>
          <p>
            We work on data analytics, engineering, and business intelligence projects of all sizes. 
            From custom dashboard development to complete analytics platform builds, we tailor our 
            services to your specific needs.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <h3>What is your typical project timeline?</h3>
          <p>
            Project timelines vary based on scope and complexity. Small projects might take 2-4 weeks, 
            while larger platforms could take 2-6 months. We'll provide a detailed timeline estimate 
            during our initial consultation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <h3>Do you offer ongoing support and maintenance?</h3>
          <p>
            Yes! We provide post-launch support, maintenance packages, and can help scale your 
            solution as your needs grow. We believe in building long-term partnerships with our clients.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <h3>Can you integrate with our existing systems?</h3>
          <p>
            Absolutely. We have experience integrating with various databases, APIs, and third-party 
            services. We'll work with your existing infrastructure to deliver seamless solutions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <h3>Do you sign NDAs and work under confidentiality agreements?</h3>
          <p>
            Yes, we're happy to sign NDAs and work under your confidentiality requirements. 
            We take data security and client privacy very seriously.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        The first step is simple - just fill out the form above or send us an email.
      </p>
      <p style="color: #6b7280;">
        No sales pressure. Just a genuine conversation about your data needs.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
